In November 2006 I reported Chelsea and their players for attempting to intimidate me during a game at Tottenham.

I asked the FA to study a specific incident, which was clear on video, when I felt intimidated and pressurised to give a decision.

The FA reviewed the footage and said as I did not look frightened or intimidated, they would not be taking the case any further.

